2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The proposed method is based on end-to-end deep convolutional neural networks, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an AI-based method for left ventricular volume estimation on CMR images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the analysis of medical images, which can be considered as a multimedia application. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed method is based on deep neural networks, which can be considered as a subfield of neural computing.
